    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验带有一丝疯狂的皇家园艺！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《Queen's Garden: French Splendor》</i> 将带您开启一段幽默的顶层社会园艺之旅。扮演皇家景观设计师，证明您拥有满足王室所需的“园艺天赋”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黄金搭档</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不会孤军奋战！<strong>见见我们的常驻专家</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/042227ce553385d6fa56702405eafa51.avif?t=1767218151\" width=875 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万寿菊 (Marigold)：</strong> 一位完美主义园丁长，她把每一片枯萎的叶子都视为对个人的侮辱，在每道树篱都达到完美对称之前绝不休息。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>弗洛里安 (Florian)：</strong> 迷人的助手，他认为的“苦差事”就是夸奖杂草生命力顽强，并躲在修剪过的灌木丛里睡长觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过比野葛生长速度还快的三消谜题，您将把一个看起来像是被龙卷风开着割草机席卷过的花园，变成一个连凡尔赛宫都会嫉妒的天堂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心游戏特色</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >110 个疯狂匹配关卡（因为 109 个关卡完全不够玩）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让普通花园小矮人显得索然无味的强力道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰一个如此精致的法式花园，连蜗牛都会戴上贝雷帽</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如此令人上瘾的游戏体验，会让您忘记太阳长什么样（对于园艺游戏来说真是讽刺）</p></li></ul>",
